items.sentence: Tom is a pal of mine.
Is it my turn to pay?
I have to go ask Tom.
I have to go get Tom.
I sleep in a big bed.
I sat down on a rock.
I got Tom to help me.
I knew it was a joke.
I love my work a lot.
Do you feel up to it?
OK, I think I got it.
I gave Tom a big hug.
We have a ways to go.
